updateDocumentWithNewItem(userId, "weekly", currentWeek(), newItemName, newItemQuantity, newExpensesValue)
updateDocumentWithNewItem(userId, "daily", currentDay(), newItemName, newItemQuantity, newExpensesValue)
```

